        <abstract> 
<p>Discusses NA’s pamphlet on human progress. Suggests making it a book [<hi rend="italic">A survey of human progress</hi> (1861)].</p> 
            <p>Comments on study of dead languages.</p>
            <p>Denies that animals are "governed only by selfish motives".</p>
